    - target: {fileID: 8514466214802780656, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "guys... can anyone please spare some fear points or offerings? Literally
        begging at this point. \r\nFor real, it\u2019s been a whole year since this
        zombie outbreak started, and my food supply is completely bone-dry. Nobody
        is scared of ghosts anymore. If I don\u2019t hit my fear point quota by next
        month, the Underworld bureaucracy is going to deport me straight back to
        Hell.  If you have any extra points or leftover soul food to share, please
        send them my way. Even a little bit helps. Love you guys...\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
