    - target: {fileID: 8304570894488040445, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Forget about getting any construction sacrifices, ever since these
        mutated pests infested my site, humans won\u2019t even set foot here. I can\u2019t
        even get a decent meal out of scaring the night shift security guards anymore.
        I'm literally starving. \r\nAnd to make things worse, these stupid bugs are
        constantly chewing through the structural steel beams. The whole framework
        is crumbling! WHERE AM I SUPPOSED TO SLEEP?! My home is literally being eaten
        away. \r\nIf there are any high-tier demons or alpha ghosts out there, PLEASE
        carry me through this raid and exterminate these iron termites. I'm begging
        you. I just want a good night's sleep.\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8667780113636253414, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
