    - target: {fileID: 8514466214802780656, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "The Underworld Council is completely unhinged. This is actual madness.
        Imagine forcing ghosts to pay taxes during a literal zombie pandemic?! Are
        they out of their minds?\r\nTaxes? Bro, bold of you to assume I even know
        where my next meal is coming from. I am out here living offering-to-offering,
        and these bureaucrats expect me to fund their luxury crypts. Look at the
        economy!\r\nBut hey, the moment we speak up and complain about it, the government
        will probably just blast us with holy water for \"inciting a riot.\" Oh no,
        I\u2019m so terrified.\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8592897770337388089, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: peak Underworld capitalism.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
