    - target: {fileID: 8514466214802780656, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Honestly, most of you in this thread are just a bunch of bitter, salty
        ghosts. Boohoo, so sad that humans care more about actual zombies than your
        basic, low-effort haunts now. \r\nLook, I\u2019m a ghost too, but if you\u2019re
        going to criticize the administration, at least have some ethics and decorum.
        Stop blindly raging in the replies. Why don't you offer some constructive
        solutions on how to handle this zombie outbreak instead of just whining?\r\nBesides,
        if you\u2019re lagging behind on your afterlife taxes, you should be grateful
        the Department of Demonic Revenues literally gave everyone a 1-month grace
        period. If you still can\u2019t pay after that, that\u2019s a textbook skill
        issue and personal accountability.\r\nImagine getting high-speed Pancagram
        network coverage subsidized by the government, and still throwing a tantrum
        when the tax bill comes due.\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8592897770337388089, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Unpopular Opinion: Your failure to generate fear points during the
        pandemic is a personal skill issue'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
