    - target: {fileID: 7994378320779858399, guid: 6b5ca361c6149524e8c0716eaa0cf829, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "The Underworld Council is completely unhinged. This is actual madness.
        Imagine forcing ghosts to pay taxes during a literal zombie pandemic?! Are
        they out of their minds?\nTaxes? Bro, bold of you to assume I even know where
        my next meal is coming from. I am out here living offering-to-offering, and
        these bureaucrats expect me to fund their luxury crypts. Look at the economy!\nBut
        hey, the moment we speak up and complain about it, the government will probably
        just blast us with holy water for \"inciting a riot.\" Oh no, I\u2019m so
        terrified.\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
