    - target: {fileID: 7994378320779858399, guid: 6b5ca361c6149524e8c0716eaa0cf829, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "WAKE UP GHOULS!!!  This whole \"zombie outbreak\" is literally just
        a giant psyop by the Underworld Elites to keep us broke in the afterlife
        forever. \nIf those Big Pharma Demon Doctors try to get you to take some
        \"vaccine\" or whatever they're calling it, DO NOT TRUST THEM! It\u2019s
        a trap! They just want to inject microchips into our ectoplasm so they can
        track our every move. \nThink about it, once your Fear Points get too high,
        they\u2019ll spawn zombies right outside your favorite haunting grounds so
        you can\u2019t get any soul food. Wake up!\nStay safe out there, brothers
        and sisters... the Illuminati is watching us.\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8199465599749998400, guid: 6b5ca361c6149524e8c0716eaa0cf829, type: 3}
