    - target: {fileID: 8304570894488040445, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Honestly, these zombies are completely crossing the line. The audacity
        of them to literally TRASH my offerings at Freaky Holiday?! Do they have
        any idea how hard I worked scaring those humans just to get that food? I
        put so much effort into my haunts, and these brainless freeloaders ruined
        it in seconds. Now the humans are too terrified to even show up. My business
        is officially dead. \r\nCan someone PLEASE pull up and evict these zombies?
        Seriously, anyone. If you go to Freaky Holiday, you\u2019ll spot them immediately\u2014they\u2019re
        literally walking around in those creepy Tung Tung mascot suits.\r\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8667780113636253414, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
